            <p><strong>Political offices</strong><br />2008-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Cabinet Minister, Ministry of Agriculture and Food, Jens Stoltenberg’s second Government<br />2008-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Acting Leader, Centre Party<br />2007-2008 Parliamentary Leader of the Centre Party in the Storting<br />2005-2007 Deputy Parliamentary Leader of the Centre Party in the Storting<br />2005-2009 Member no. 3 of the Storting, representing Nord-Trøndelag<br />2003-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; First Deputy Chairman, Centre Party central party organisation<br />2001-2005 Deputy Member no. 1 of the Storting, representing Nord-Trøndelag <br />2000&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Cabinet Minister, Ministry of Fisheries<br />1997-1999 Deputy Mayor, Vikna Municipality<br />1993-1997 Deputy Member no. 1 of the Storting, representing Nord-Trøndelag<br />1993-1997 First Deputy Chairman, Centre Party central party organisation<br />1992-1997 Mayor, Vikna Municipality<br />1989-1993 Deputy Member no. 4 of the Storting, representing Nord-Trøndelag <br />1985-1986 Political Adviser, Ministry of Fisheries</p>
<p><strong>Membership of Storting Standing Committees and delegations</strong><br />2007-2008 Member of the Enlarged Foreign Affairs Committee <br />2007-2008 Member of the Standing Committee on Scrutiny and Constitutional Affairs&nbsp; <br />2007-2008 Member of the Election Committee<br />2005-2007 Chairman of the Standing Committee on Business and Industry<br />2005-2009 Deputy Member of the Storting delegation to the NATO Parliamentary Assembly</p>
